			<div class="bt_bb_wrapper"><section id="bt_bb_section645d054eeaac7"  class="bt_bb_section bt_bb_layout_boxed_1200 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_top_spacing_large bt_bb_bottom_spacing_large"  data-bt-override-class="null"><div class="bt_bb_port"><div class="bt_bb_cell"><div class="bt_bb_cell_inner"><div class="bt_bb_row_wrapper"><div  class="bt_bb_row bt_bb_column_gap_40"  data-bt-override-class="{}"><div  class="bt_bb_column col-xl-6 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_padding_normal"  data-width="6" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><header class="bt_bb_headline bt_bb_dash_top bt_bb_superheadline bt_bb_size_large bt_bb_align_inherit" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_size_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_size_large&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;large&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_inherit&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;}}"><h3 class="bt_bb_headline_tag"><span class="bt_bb_headline_superheadline">WHERE CAN WE HELP?</span><span class="bt_bb_headline_content"><span><b>In Commercial &</b><br />
<u>Residential Areas</u></span></span></h3></header><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_top_spacing_normal" data-bt-override-class="null"></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion bt_bb_color_scheme_5 bt_bb_style_simple bt_bb_shape_round" style="; --accordion-primary-color:#191919; --accordion-secondary-color:#e29a2d;"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What is the procedure of a visit by one of the pest control experts?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As soon as your appointment is scheduled, we will send an experienced and certified professional, who will decide on the type of poison and bait to be used, depending on the pest. You will also receive Risk and COSHH assessments (if applicable) and a written report with information about the service.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">Do you handle domestic and commercial premises?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yes, we work with all kinds of clients and properties.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">How quickly will you respond to my problem and how soon can my home be treated?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our client care center operates 24 hours for your convenience; you can call any time for questions or bookings. Usually we can be there within the hour, if not certainly on the same day. However, if the nearest appointment available is a couple of days, we will provide you with information on how to deal with the problem in the meantime.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What will a pest control technician do when they visit my property?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our Pest Control Technician will inspect your property; evaluate damages and explain the size of your infestation. Afterwards, he or she will treat the affected areas and provide you with advice on how to prevent re-infestations.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">Do I have to leave my home when it’s being treated?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Depending on the treatment, if it involves spraying you have to leave the space where sprays are being applied for at least two hours. However, you will be instructed beforehand according to your pest control service.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal bt_bb_hidden_md bt_bb_hidden_lg" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div><div  class="bt_bb_column col-xl-6 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_padding_normal"  data-width="6" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_image bt_bb_shape_square bt_bb_target_self bt_bb_align_inherit bt_bb_hover_style_simple bt_bb_content_display_always bt_bb_content_align_middle bt_bb_fill_background_color_full" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_inherit&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;}}"><span><img width="640" height="640" src="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-640x640.png" class="attachment-boldthemes_medium_square size-boldthemes_medium_square" alt="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-640x640.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" data-full_image_src="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1.png" title="Untitled-1Artboard-1" srcset="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-640x640.png 640w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-160x160.png 160w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-768x768.png 768w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1-320x320.png 320w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-1.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></span></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal bt_bb_hidden_md bt_bb_hidden_lg" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="bt_bb_section645d054eeb6ec"  class="bt_bb_section bt_bb_layout_boxed_1200 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_section_show_right_boxed_content"  data-bt-override-class="null"><div class="bt_bb_port"><div class="bt_bb_cell"><div class="bt_bb_cell_inner"><div class="bt_bb_row_wrapper"><div  class="bt_bb_row"  data-bt-override-class="{}"><div  class="bt_bb_column col-xl-6 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_mobile_align_to_left_edge bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate"  data-width="6" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_image bt_bb_shape_square bt_bb_target_self bt_bb_align_right bt_bb_hover_style_simple bt_bb_content_display_always bt_bb_content_align_middle bt_bb_fill_background_color_full" data-bt-override-class="{&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_right&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;right&quot;}}"><span><img width="640" height="640" src="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-640x640.png" class="attachment-boldthemes_medium_square size-boldthemes_medium_square" alt="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-640x640.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" data-full_image_src="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2.png" title="Untitled-1Artboard-2" srcset="{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-640x640.png 640w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-160x160.png 160w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-768x768.png 768w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2-320x320.png 320w, {{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Untitled-1Artboard-2.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></span></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_normal bt_bb_hidden_md bt_bb_hidden_lg" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div><div  class="bt_bb_column col-xl-6 bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate bt_bb_padding_double btLazyLoadBackground bt_bb_column_background_image bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate" style="background-image:url(https_/waspsrats.com/wp-content/plugins/bold-page-builder/img/blank.html);background-position:right top;background-size:50%;" data-background_image_src='{{ asset('/') }}wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bgn-people.png' data-width="6" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="null"></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion bt_bb_color_scheme_5 bt_bb_style_simple bt_bb_shape_round" style="; --accordion-primary-color:#191919; --accordion-secondary-color:#e29a2d;"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What kind of training have the pest technicians passed?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-1" class="comp mntl-sc-block finance-sc-block-html mntl-sc-block-html">
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The exterminators working for Waspsrats have passed the Safe Use of Pesticides, BPCA Training courses.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">Do I need to treat my property monthly?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">No, you don’t. The technicians have a strict schedule when treatments are needed. In no case are monthly visits required.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What do I need to do before a bed bug treatment?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Remove all bedding and linens, sheets, pillowcases, duvet covers, etc. Bag them all up in the same room so the infestation doesn’t spread to the rest of the house. Hot wash on 60-90′ C. Proceed doing the same with clothing around or under the affected areas, especially items stored under the bed –must be emptied and their content must also be hot washed. Hoover meticulously covered all areas of the bedroom including both sides of the mattresses. You will be provided with further instructions before and after the scheduled bed bugs treatment.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">How to book a service with you?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We provide the following options to our clients:</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you only want to receive a quote, go to our contact form.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Got any additional questions? Call us 24/7 on our number 7521 803008 </span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">Do you offer same-day service?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yes, Wasprats Pest Control does offer a same day emergency treatment when you need to take action as soon as possible.You can reach us 24/7 and we can send a pest exterminator to your property within one hour.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">Is your pest control products safe for babies?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Depending on the type of insecticide and its application, it would be best for you and the baby to remain out of the treated premises for a couple of hours.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What type of chemicals does your company use?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The chemicals we use are certified and of high quality.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item"><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_title">What pests do you treat?</div><div class="bt_bb_accordion_item_content"><div  class="bt_bb_text" >
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We treat bed bugs, mice, rats, wasps, fleas, moths, cockroaches, ants, spiders, silverfish, flies, woodworm, dust mites, carpet beetles and other insects that offer fumigation treatment.</span></p>
</div>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div>		</div><!-- /boldthemes_content -->
 
